grateful to you, Team Leader Lee.

804
01:01:42,640 --> 01:01:46,100
You got me Seo Hye Jin's files and everything.

805
01:01:46,100 --> 01:01:49,080
But...

806
01:01:49,080 --> 01:01:53,400
shouldn't you be thankful to me, too?

807
01:01:54,620 --> 01:01:57,260
You lost your students to the international school teacher Choeseon Korean hired

808
01:01:57,260 --> 01:02:00,550
and lost a whole class, but I forgave you.

809
01:02:00,550 --> 01:02:04,640
And I stopped Director Kim from adjusting the rate of pay, too.

810
01:02:04,640 --> 01:02:06,580
