811
01:02:06,580 --> 01:02:08,210
Assistant Director.

812
01:02:08,210 --> 01:02:10,600
Everyone already knows

813
01:02:10,600 --> 01:02:13,790
that you're my person.

814
01:02:13,790 --> 01:02:16,610
And they know we never liked Seo Hye Jin, too. But,

815
01:02:16,610 --> 01:02:20,880
if you spread a rumor about Seo Hye Jin and Lee Jun Ho,

816
01:02:20,880 --> 01:02:23,970
how believable would that be?

817
01:02:27,240 --> 01:02:31,020
