819
01:02:39,820 --> 01:02:41,810
I understand.

820
01:02:44,610 --> 01:02:49,500
What if we say she dated him since he was a minor...

821
01:02:49,500 --> 01:02:51,660
Is that too much?

822
01:02:54,750 --> 01:02:59,310
You would've been better at writing fiction

823
01:02:59,310 --> 01:03:02,760
